{"tid":1557631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Twitter] 有手足整咗個五毛report list！","createTime":"2019-09-10T07:50:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T17:34:06.000Z","uid":69395,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"364732c2fff463bef96af4b9e70e08df6cafdb43","tid":1557631,"uid":69395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:50:23.000Z","msg":"(個list唔係我整嘅，只係見到幫手share畀大家睇。)<br />\n(多謝JK_茉莉君手足，唔係佢我都唔知有呢個list存在！)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fv6Mecg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFv6Mecg.png&h=e58fbf23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/kNjamLX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/kNjamLX</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">各位Twitter手足請注意！！<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n話說原來Twitter一位叫AntiPropaganda嘅手足幾日前整咗個五毛list：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ln9U7uH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLn9U7uH.png&h=fd70b784&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/AntiPropagranda/status/1169601599418748935?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAntiPropagranda%2Fstatus%2F1169601599418748935%3Fs%3D19&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=9279afb4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAntiPropagranda%2Fstatus%2F1169601599418748935%3Fs%3D19&h=17fa09f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/AntiPropagranda/status/1169601599418748935?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">已FC Twitter五毛list (內含report五毛教學及twitter文宣攻略，有玩twitter嘅手足必睇)：</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Rt2xPTLkrY3E9U9rtIlXx0bgmrQKqO86VZGUe9_6cRg/edit#gid=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1Rt2xPTLkrY3E9U9rtIlXx0bgmrQKqO86VZGUe9_6cRg%2Fedit%23gid%3D0&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=79ff800d\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Rt2xPTLkrY3E9U9rtIlXx0bgmrQKqO86VZGUe9_6cRg/edit#gid=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公海五毛twitter list (未FC，各位手足有懷疑都可以擺上去，會有人跟進)：</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1gWpYMeCm176NSjkg-lDahh9OuzW7Jv_7m7onHDN0cGY/edit#gid=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1gWpYMeCm176NSjkg-lDahh9OuzW7Jv_7m7onHDN0cGY%2Fedit%23gid%3D0&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=6d819d62\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1gWpYMeCm176NSjkg-lDahh9OuzW7Jv_7m7onHDN0cGY/edit#gid=0</a><br />\n<br />\n最後，其實twitter都有個專用hashtag <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#五毛報串組</span></strong> 畀各位手足report五毛ac。我之前都係用呢個hashtag。<br />\n<br />\n各位手足，加油呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063f8b83279581d7c4f8742fd2b9368a0102da9b","tid":1557631,"uid":69395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:51:23.000Z","msg":"推呀！"},{"pid":"e9496b383e0e40ce6b9d1e32de60c88b56680174","tid":1557631,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:52:00.000Z","msg":"Push <br />\n最新活動：唱民主聖歌，傳福音！<br />\n手足每晚都好努力貼連儂，但凌晨3-6就比人清！<br />\n913 914 915 活動要去，但請起返連儂牆<br />\n<ins>考驗毅力與堅持</ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">做更具價值嘅野</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">等所有人知道發生緊咩事先！</span></span></strong><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">連儂牆起源於反共，呢條戰線不能倒！</code></pre><br />\n勇武走得太前，做人要有公關！<br />\n文宣多一個就好多！連儂牆要人！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一場抗爭/革命搞十年八載唔出奇<br />\n<strong>衛城革命，生活抗爭；拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；</strong><br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">幫襯</span>良心小店<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">抵制</span>「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n3. 安全之下，<span style=\"color: red;\">免費港鐵</span>；二人同遊，一人免費；買平飛；長者八達通<br />\n4. 夜晚<span style=\"color: red;\">十點？九點？吶喊</span>！！！（fact checking)<br />\n5. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: red;\">每日一post</span>，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=e2ff5e43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n7. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n8. 保持<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立思考</span>，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour ，五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">低消費</span>，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">做孝子救港</span>，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆</span>貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股，MPF都買美股<br />\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會事務，做陪審員、派傳單、放映會<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.10"},{"pid":"2d1b9e701ef93a4efb5cfe133b8c89e7800e5823","tid":1557631,"uid":69395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:59:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81a816af5e4b4da577a4ce5cb387b4c0fbfd6518","tid":1557631,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:02:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2655d3fcc8c51ffa77ca947756a6a38650088d9a","tid":1557631,"uid":69395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:05:51.000Z","msg":"有玩twitter嘅手足必睇呀！！！！！！"},{"pid":"675e1cc754e71d9d4e18896212edadbf26d6d862","tid