a628167028a08ab5fac271ed34dcca8a8baf63","tid":1557631,"uid":69395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2aa903ca27b055e69228ee2f6d9b5b914a62b4c","tid":1557631,"uid":266045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:12:08.000Z","msg":"估唔到就算唔係P牌都要自己推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唉<br />\n我就算喺度留言都係推唔到po<br />\n好無奈。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:17:28.000Z","msg":"有更重要嘅post要推，我明白嘅<br />\n我會定期推post"},{"pid":"5d8560de55e32b63affabcfcad8b20cdeb670550","tid":1557631,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:09:55.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n如果發現twitter五毛藍絲就打上去"},{"pid":"1c3621cb8313b4a941a0d7f9ad04885bba396f29","tid":1557631,"uid":69395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:21:14.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推，路過而有玩/準備玩twitter嘅麻煩望望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2ecc67e188c09188e1207c67c179b754ee2d599","tid":1557631,"uid":91558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:17:37.000Z","msg":"外國勢力同樣重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請即參與：<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>#wtsappforhk campaign (#eye4hk 2.0)</strong></span><br />\n有twitter既快啲retweet，無twitter既而家開番個<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>本地線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 將警暴，藍絲，官員，議員罪證狂推比警察<br />\n2. 為左令每一個負責mon住既阿sir都不愁寂莫，每個人睇番自己生日日子既最後一位數字，揀下表有同樣最尾位數字既電話<br />\n3. 有關如何保護自己，請搜尋「太空」等相關字眼<br />\n<br />\n5566 9500<br />\n5566 9501<br />\n5566 9502<br />\n5566 9503<br />\n5566 9504<br />\n5566 9505<br />\n5566 9506<br />\n5566 9507<br />\n5566 9508<br />\n5566 9509<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>國際線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1. retweet手足既呢條tweet, 記住comment加#wtsappforhk<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hongkongers8/status/1171379846447919104?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhongkongers8%2Fstatus%2F1171379846447919104%3Fs%3D21&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=b0411a18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhongkongers8%2Fstatus%2F1171379846447919104%3Fs%3D21&h=44f2ff93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hongkongers8/status/1171379846447919104?s=21</a><br />\n2. 如果你選擇將10個電話重新打一次出黎，記得加+852<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1. 成本低<br />\n2. 可以迫大家儲下唔同角度文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n壞處：<br />\n1. 本地線唔會要大家post番個舉報cap圖出黎，少左第二次marketing機會 (which is fine)<br />\n2. 外國人參與國際線程度成疑，但我覺得以campaign之名，行宣傳之實。就咁講#chinazi，#culturalrevolution，老實講有d悶。"},{"pid":"7d3f96f4ee7cdc8d781c010e4c529acfc976a7ae","tid":1557631,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d2f2e50e82e25652796927b51deba68c33a2a4","tid":1557631,"uid":277084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:48:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9f87d03aa3c30f843f35ec41b8384c9fef1514a7","tid":1557631,"uid":260460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:55:32.000Z","msg":"好野冇人推"},{"pid":"3caf36f7e463db8486f0269ebb5c70aa49ece0db","tid":1557631,"uid":69395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2ecc67e188c09188e1207c67c179b754ee2d599","tid":1557631,"uid":91558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:17:37.000Z","msg":"外國勢力同樣重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請即參與：<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>#wtsappforhk campaign (#eye4hk 2.0)</strong></span><br />\n有twitter既快啲retweet，無twitter既而家開番個<b